tldr: The user requested a review of a sleep questionnaire application against
  detailed acceptance criteria. The agent identified several missing features
  and then implemented them, including a tiredness severity scale, COMISA and
  insufficient sleep syndrome detection, weighted EDS scoring, and outbound
